                These symptoms typically start within 2-4 days of stopping and can last 1-3 weeks:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Flu-like symptoms (fatigue, muscle aches)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Dizziness or vertigo</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>"Brain zaps" or electric shock sensations</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Nausea, vomiting, diarrhea</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Irritability, anxiety, or mood swings</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <AlertCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Sleep disturbances or vivid dreams</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
